{
  "stem": "1363.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Budapest, very close, where in one of the church-- synagogue's backyard, in a-- in a complex where there was a garden raised-- not even garden part, but a, a-- how shall I say what it is?",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's concreted.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So it was-- a yard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But it was no flowers or no greenery, like a school yard, right?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where kids march up and down, or whatever they do.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in that-- and there were rooms around that yard where we were sleeping.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, there happened something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was, as I said, 16 going onto 17.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my brother was a year younger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And every day there were, I think, weekly, changing overseers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're not necessarily Nazis.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They weren't Germans.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They were Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they were employed by the government to oversee these few hundred or whatever Jews were there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were the youngest, Freddie and I.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were other-- people who didn't-- who were not citizens of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Nowhere.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were Nansen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was called Nansen.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were stateless.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They could do with us whatever they wanted because we did not belong to Hungary or to Austria, where my father came from.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we didn't belong to any other country.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We lived in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We were born in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we weren't citizens of Hungary.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Right.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So there was, as I said from government, employed detectives, as we called them, who were watching the main gate so that we-- who were in that school yard, do not walk out.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was a man.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was-- can't emphasize.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was 16 going onto 17.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he must have been around about 30.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I can't recall him exactly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And well, he said to me, if I come to his apartment home, he'll take me out.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
